{"tid":2104641,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"鋪天蓋地的氛圍 - 蔣芸","createTime":"2020-07-12T06:16:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-12T06:16:58.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"943174089eb0dcbeb731853d7d8ecf06365c2da8","tid":2104641,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T06:16:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E8%94%A3%E8%8A%B8/daily/article/20200712/20954129/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E8%2594%25A3%25E8%258A%25B8%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200712%2F20954129%2F&d=GdzNT1%2FdEV%2FiwqmWSoLNnma%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=d90e200c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E8%2594%25A3%25E8%258A%25B8%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200712%2F20954129%2F&h=dc12b52f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E8%94%A3%E8%8A%B8/daily/article/20200712/20954129/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n鋪天蓋地的氛圍 - 蔣芸<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200712/large/1594452733_44ab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200712%2Flarge%2F1594452733_44ab.jpg&h=af4cf863&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n各大專院校法律系的教授、學者們無不對於港版國安法認真研究，因為莘莘學子們的疑問太多，還要應付各界的詢問，人們已不相信政府官員口徑一致的釋法之說，要解釋這一項橫空出世草草降臨於我城的法律並不是件容易的事；先造成事實，再來撇清的做法更令人反感。<br />\n<br />\n最為人詬病的是整個立法的過程；不需在<br />\n。。。。。<br />\n而且無王管的狀態，一於放手任他們狂舞。<br />\n<br />\n兩地到現在尚未完全通關，<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n令人駭然。<br />\n<br />\n一些標語口號金句頃刻間成為禁忌，<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n吾不欲觀之，誰又欲觀之。 <br />\n<br />\n蔣芸<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"}]}